instructions: Put the Charger on the table
Put the dinner fork to the left of the charger with the prongs pointing up
Put the dinner knife to the right of the charger with the blade pointing up
Put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with the prongs pointing up
Put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife with the blade pointing up
Put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife with the bowl pointing up
Put the dessert spoon above the charger with the bowl pointing left
Put the dessert fork below the dessert spoon with the prongs pointing right
Put the bread plate above the forks
Put the butter knife on top of the bread plate
Put the water glass above the knives
Put the napkin on top of the plate
